title: Handbook of Greek Pottery (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
New York Graphic Society | 1967 | English | 240 pages | PDF | 40 MB

There are many books on Greek pottery for the specialist, and there are also books on certain aspects of Greek pottery that are designed for a wider public. But so far a comprehensive guide for the layman has been lacking, in spite of the increasing interest that is being shown in ancient Greece today. Mr. Folsom's Handbook of Greek Pottery will therefore meet a growing need
